attributes.title: horrible app
attributes.review: i downloaded this app in hopes i could see what our president was up to, but all the app did was glitch out every time i opened it. however, on the last full moon i opened the app once more. the app showed me a black screen with the words, “don’t turn on the lights” i proceeded to say, “haha no❤️” our loud. i got up and turned on the lights. i looked into my living room, and i felt my soul leave my body. there standing in the middle of my living room was a life-sized cheeto with blond hair. i screamed, and went to run to the front door. i was stopped by the cheeto. he wasn’t touching me though, he just had his hand out in my direction. i gasped. “no way. you can use the force?” i asked. “yes. i have taken the souls from all my children and given myself the force.” the cheeto cackled. “even barron?” i asked. “yes. i caught him trying to escape, and i couldn’t let that happen.” i cried out for barron, the only boy my age who i would ever simp for. “now i will take your soul.” i yelled for help, hoping someone would hear me. just then my 3-legged, talking dog ran into the room. “what’s going on?” he said, in an australian accent. “this cheeto is trying to kill me!” i yelled. “haha good thing i like cheetos.” he laughed. my dog proceeded to eat the cheeto. after he finished he looked at me. “what type of cheeto was that? it tasted horrible.” he the proceeded to puke out a bunch of wispy, ghost-looking things. “gasp. the souls of the cheeto’s children. we must return them.” my dog looked at me, ashamed that i just said gasp out loud. i returned the souls, and the cheeto’s kids went on to live great lives. i told barron, “BE BE BE MY BFF CUZ IDK WHATS COMING NEXT LMHO WITH THE REST SO TTYL XOX” and now we are bestfriends forever. however, my dog got a very bad stomachache from the cheeto, and now he has an american accent, so therefore this app is horrible.
